		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />MIDI got a bad reputation back when PC computers had sound cards capable of playing midi files, but not capable of using high quality "sound fonts".  So you would have a really nice song sound like a bunch of bleeps and bloops on these cheap PCs.

		

