<br />
<br />Though granted...  I don't know the details of .mid and how it works interally -- I'm not going to believe the pro-midi banter everyone spouts until I hear it for myself.  And so far I haven't.  And until I do... I say:
<br />
<br /><strong>MIDI SUCKS</strong>

		

