		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Memblers wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">MIDI is really only good for what it's supposed to be - a 'Musical Instrument Digital Interface'.</div>
<br />So what's the Interface for sending Digital audio sample banks to Digital Musical Instruments? There's the "Sample Dump Standard" that runs as a SysEx over MIDI, but I don't see wide support, especially given that the maximum data rate of MIDI is 25 kbps (not counting start/stop bits).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
